m h dom dom mon dow
*/5 * * * * /home/user/bin/makehappy.sh - run makehappy.sh every 5 minutes
15 */2 * * /home/user/bin/makehappy.sh - run makehappy.sh at 0:15, 2:15, 4:15, etc
27 10,13 * * 1,4 /home/user/bin/makehappy.sh - run makehappy.sh on monday and thursday at 10:27 and 13:27

m - minute
h - hour
dom - day of month
mon - month
dow - day of week
